text: The UniCredit Țiriac Bank headquarters is a class A office building located in the city of Bucharest, Romania. The project consists of one 64 meter-tall with 15 floor building, with a total surface area of 28,000 m2 (6,000 m2 below ground level and 22,000 m2 above ground). == References == Category:Skyscraper office buildings in Bucharest Category:Romanian building and structure stubs Category:Office buildings completed in 2012
title: Unicredit Tower Bucharest
